# Type:
# feat          -> new feature
# improvement   -> feature improvement
# fix           -> bug fix
# refactor      -> internal improvement
# docs          -> documentation
# test          -> tests
# chore         -> maintenance
#
# Scope:
# projet        -> full projet (ex: tree change)
# className     -> class change, or new method...
# folderName    -> new folder with new class
# 
# [type]<scope>: ...
[]<>: ...
